title: Space Jerks
description:
Space Jerks, written by Sean Clements. Stone Cold Fox at Maude Night, UCBTNY, March 10, 2008.

Starring Scott Courlander, D'Arcy Erokan, Nate Lang, & Joe Spellman. Directed by Dominic Dierkes.
